zh.EdgeMap.PatchMapping.072081-1: 采集器的点位名称与属性名称一致时将自动映射绑定；有多个采集器点位名称与属性名称一致时以第1个采集器的点位数据进行绑定

en.EdgeMap.PatchMapping.072081-1: If the point name of the collector is the same as the attribute name, the system automatically maps and binds the collector. If multiple collector point names are the same as the attribute names, bind the point data of the first collector
en.EdgeMap.PatchMapping.072081-8: There is no mapping for the corresponding attribute
